Blurb::
Define the vector by initial and final points
Description::
List the final values for each variable.
The vector's direction and magnitude are determined by the initial value
from the variables specification, and the \c final_point.

The actual points are determined based on the this vector and the number of steps.
of points chosen in \c num_points.
